{"tid":2530730,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警務處副處長蕭澤頤與警犬示範做平板支撐 曹永廉宋芝齡同參與","createTime":"2021-05-14T15:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-14T16:41:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"56d17cf9fea1e8f49215f2b4fcadb4bca29cea1f","tid":2530730,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T15:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/none/2839b8bdd46b39e5ee1958827cb1c4dd/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210514/_2021051420383546968.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F2839b8bdd46b39e5ee1958827cb1c4dd%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210514%2F_2021051420383546968.jpeg&h=8dec47d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/432p0/0x0/100/none/7db05e13d8e747f3018ee4d2f67afe37/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210514/_2021051420383242881.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F432p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F7db05e13d8e747f3018ee4d2f67afe37%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210514%2F_2021051420383242881.jpeg&h=7c730c4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/432p0/0x0/100/none/c4014a11ed3ac7626a1da992ccd5bc6d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210514/_2021051420383440315.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F432p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2Fc4014a11ed3ac7626a1da992ccd5bc6d%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210514%2F_2021051420383440315.jpeg&h=102b737a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/432p0/0x0/100/none/5ac43820f80b383c4305e113fadd3ae9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210514/_2021051420383921390.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F432p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F5ac43820f80b383c4305e113fadd3ae9%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210514%2F_2021051420383921390.jpeg&h=4deaab63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/432p0/0x0/100/none/83da31b09bba914624e85215933fd7df/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210514/_2021051420384050306.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F432p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F83da31b09bba914624e85215933fd7df%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210514%2F_2021051420384050306.jpeg&h=720f5ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警隊為鼓勵更多市民支持及協助打擊殘酷對待動物的行為，現正推展「動物守護‧社區大使」計劃，並舉行「我撐動物挑戰賽」以宣揚人與動物互相支持的訊息。副處長（行動）蕭澤頤在挑戰賽的示範短片中與警犬示範作不同的平板及互動方法。<br />\n<br />\n挑戰賽邀請大眾發揮創意，創作一個「人寵合一」的平板支撐動作。蕭澤頤日前與警犬隊成員一同拍攝挑戰賽的示範短片，做出平板及互動動作，同時與警犬互動。<br />\n<br />\n挑戰賽已經於5月初開展，參加挑戰賽之人士包括有藝人曹永廉及宋芝齡、學校、少年警訊會員及耆樂警訊會員等。短片中除了有巡邏犬，亦有守護之星Sunny及Zander參與拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n市民若想參與挑戰賽，只需寵物維持15秒或以上的平板支撐動作，將過程拍攝下來並將短片上載至Facebook或Instagram，內文標注「#我撐動物」並邀請3位朋友一同參與便可。評審會根據人寵的配合度、創意以及帶出的訊息以選出得獎作品。"},{"pid":"f30b6cf8e82f1c2438098f387ab14c493b6b406e","tid":2530730,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T15:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4da9d86218b82309b5ea9a45714ba9eaeb8aa7","tid":2530730,"uid":39710,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T15:38:41.000Z","msg":"臭閪藍狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d22aa770b7127e371da68790b37d10971f3dd1","tid":2530730,"uid":353587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"啲圖全部狗嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im